{"tid":1983854,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[幫人開][M記]停止二元對立，不批鬥不等於正名化","createTime":"2020-04-22T05:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T03:21:14.000Z","uid":150100,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e1bb7a5c3dab7c22f7740dcb4133401bfd0b8391","tid":1983854,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:47:08.000Z","msg":"小妹自從八月頭已經罷藍，九月中到停學前更加全職食黃店，一日洗費大概係二百蚊兩餐，屋企紙巾都買台灣製造，並且改用巴士cut埋垃圾通。直到前日...<br />\n<br />\n就係最近，我見到大家話可以食啦！老老實實，我開始懷疑自己呢半年為左咩。我就食左我半年黎第一餐藍店，食完之後我好似明白左啲嘢。<br />\n<br />\n原來就算大家話食得，我都係會內疚，因為原來我已經黃到打從心底討厭着食藍店，當你真正相信信念嗰下，為貫徹自己信念付出本來就係獎賞，我好自豪自己付出過。<br />\n<br />\n食藍店係一件壞事，最理想係人人都罷藍撐黃，呢個係目標。但係批鬥佢地係不智嘅，大家都係成年人啦，當佢認為係適當地使用藍店佢地就會用，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n以批鬥做手法係本末倒置，就好似女朋友無安全感而你就鬧佢點解唔相信你一樣，正確嘅做法係做好自己令女朋友相信自己。<br />\n<br />\n應用係藍店亦一樣，我哋要做嘅係做好自己，令人相信應該罷藍撐黃，令人打從心底想付出同投入，而唔係因爲唔做會俾人鬧。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家緊記，革命不可遠離民眾。<br />\n目標一定係撐黃罷藍，唔批鬥係因為手法錯誤，<br />\n但係絕對唔可以因此正名化食藍店。<br />\n唔批鬥唔代表食藍店係正確，唔好再二元對立<br />\n正如教育一樣，我哋必須灌溉正確嘅價值觀，但係請以鼓勵嘅形式而非痛打。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上內容不代表本人立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩搵佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5qsLRip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5qsLRip.jpg&h=735e1336&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a2a29498ab6ae57c9adacc10bdbe295250356cb","tid":1983854,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"拉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a42284a1583c9dedf51e6a154b1544632030c0","tid":1983854,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a2a29498ab6ae57c9adacc10bdbe295250356cb","tid":1983854,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"拉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"唔好啦"},{"pid":"9dcf8b0d6b67df04416db0baae23dbb083bd375f","tid":1983854,"uid":106882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d90ba49ca7fc36a0365df6815e0d5eecdbdaba6","tid":1983854,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dcf8b0d6b67df04416db0baae23dbb083bd375f","tid":1983854,"uid":106882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"甘蔗🍐"},{"pid":"b33817dcc62dc622a2111d6ef63b47631f9b6fbd","tid":1983854,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d90ba49ca7fc36a0365df6815e0d5eecdbdaba6","tid":1983854,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dcf8b0d6b67df04416db0baae23dbb083bd375f","tid":1983854,"uid":106882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"甘蔗🍐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"你個垃圾po冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206ecb225eed4b8bfaab03d902a8e4063d63acfb","tid":1983854,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b33817dcc62dc622a2111d6ef63b47631f9b6fbd","tid":1983854,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d90ba49ca7fc36a0365df6815e0d5eecdbdaba6","tid":1983854,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dcf8b0d6b67df04416db0baae23dbb083bd375f","tid":1983854,"uid":106882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"甘蔗🍐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"你個垃圾po冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:05:49.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class